      <title>雄狮电气因收入失误、现金余额减少而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/lion-electric-drops-on-revenue-miss-dwindling-cash-balance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电动汽车制造商狮子电气公司 (Lion Electric Co.) 的营收未达到预期且现金余额下降，导致该公司股价下跌 10.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/lion-electric-drops-on-revenue-miss-dwindling-cash-balance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 18:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
